{
  "stem": "5559.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In high school, we experience anti-Semitism because that was already in the '30s, early '30s-- although, Hitler wasn't in Romania, but the Romanian government was influenced by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we experienced anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We experienced someone to beat you up, or something like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the Jewish boys were sticking together, because we were all the time organized in Jewish organization, which one was called the Revisionists, it's a Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's, at that time, the famous Dr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Jabotinsky and that is actually calling, at the present, the formerly [NON-ENGLISH] That is the same, the formerly [INAUDIBLE] government of Israel, under-- formerly under Begin and then under Shamir.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were organized in this as youngsters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were taught that, in order to succeed, and quote unquote, 'to survive,' it's good to say a prayer to God, but you also have to defend yourself.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In other words, pray, you can put on [NON-ENGLISH], which you put on your left hand.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But your right hand should also be able to hold a gun, or whatever it takes to defend.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you ever have any contact from Jewish people in other countries?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish people other country, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we still had some uncles and cousin left in Vienna, Austria.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they came to visit us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, definitely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember even their name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some were of the Rosen family for my grandfather's side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some, I remember one of the name, Green-- Greenspan, something like.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They came to visit and very, we really had a fantastic time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then before the war started, God knows where they were or what's happened to them, also.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we had-- yeah from foreign countries, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure, my hobbies were like European first.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There wasn't a boy shouldn't play soccer.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
